  "metadata" : {
    "role" : "collection",
    "title" : "Migrating to Swift 6"
  },
  "primaryContentSections" : [
    {
      "content" : [
        {
          "anchor" : "Overview",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Overview",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Swift’s concurrency system, introduced in ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "https:\/\/www.swift.org\/blog\/swift-5.5-released\/",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : ",",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "makes asynchronous and parallel code easier to write and understand.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "With the Swift 6 language mode, the compiler can now",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "guarantee that concurrent programs are free of data races.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "When enabled, compiler safety checks that were",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "previously optional become required.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Adopting the Swift 6 language mode is entirely under your control",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "on a per-target basis.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "Targets that build with previous modes, as well as code in other",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "languages exposed to Swift, can all interoperate with",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "modules that have been migrated to the Swift 6 language mode.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "It is possible you have been incrementally adopting concurrency features",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "as they were introduced.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "Or, you may have been waiting for the Swift 6 release to begin using them.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "Regardless of where your project is in this process, this guide provides",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "concepts and practical help to ease the migration.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "You will find articles and code examples here that:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Explain the concepts used by Swift’s data-race safety model.",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Outline a possible way to get started with migration.",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Show how to enable complete concurrency checking for Swift 5 projects.",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Demonstrate how to enable the Swift 6 language mode.",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Present strategies to resolve common problems.",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Provide techniques for incremental adoption.",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type" : "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "content" : [
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "The Swift 6 language mode is ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "opt-in",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "emphasis"
                },
                {
                  "text" : ".",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : " ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : "Existing projects will not switch to this mode without configuration changes.",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "paragraph"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "There is a distinction between the ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "compiler version",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "emphasis"
                },
                {
                  "text" : " and ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "language mode",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "emphasis"
                },
                {
                  "text" : ".",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : " ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : "The Swift 6 compiler supports four distinct language modes: “6”, “5”, “4.2”,",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : " ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : "and “4”.",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name" : "Important",
          "style" : "important",
          "type" : "aside"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Contributing",
          "level" : 3,
          "text" : "Contributing",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "This guide is under active development. You can view the source, see",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "full code examples, and learn about how to contribute in the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "https:\/\/github.com\/apple\/swift-migration-guide",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : ".",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "We would love your contributions in the form of:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Filing ",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier" : "https:\/\/github.com\/apple\/swift-migration-guide\/issues",
                      "isActive" : true,
                      "type" : "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " to cover specific code patterns or additional sections of the guide",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Opening pull requests to improve existing content or add new content",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Reviewing others’ ",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier" : "https:\/\/github.com\/apple\/swift-migration-guide\/pulls",
                      "isActive" : true,
                      "type" : "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " for clarity and correctness of writing and code examples",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type" : "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "For more information, see the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "https:\/\/github.com\/apple\/swift-migration-guide\/blob\/main\/CONTRIBUTING.md",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " document.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind" : "content"
    }
